UID:-KVImhRXFXf2Rt7ZkIKQU
SUMMARY:Bollywood & Bhangra Dance
DTSTAMP:20260618T101508Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20260620T080000
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to move\, sweat\, and dance in this fitness-based dan
	ce class inspired by the vibrant rhythms of Bollywood and the powerful bea
	ts of Bhangra. Designed for all ages\, abilities\, and experience levels\,
	 this class welcomes everyone — whether you’re stepping onto the dance flo
	or for the first time or already love to dance. \n  \n  \n \n\nhttps://www
	.levyparkhouston.org/events/bollywood-bhangra-dance-2-2-4-2/2026-06-17/\n\
	nFrom Levy Park Houston
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/bollywood-bhangra-dance-2-2-4-2/
	2026-06-17/
LOCATION:Levy Park (Event Pavilion)\, TX
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:levy-park-houston
CATEGORIES:Levy Park Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
